### Test Messaging and Notifications API Endpoints
### Make sure to replace the base URL and token with your actual values

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### 1. Test Get Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Test Get Conversation with User
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversation/user123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Test Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverId": "user123",
  "content": "Hello! This is a test message.",
  "type": 1
}

### 4. Test Send Message with Invalid Data (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverId": "",
  "content": "",
  "type": 1
}

### 5. Test Send Message to Self (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverId": "current-user-id",
  "content": "Trying to send to myself",
  "type": 1
}

### 6. Test Mark Messages as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/messages/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": "user123"
}

### 7. Test Get Unread Message Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Test Get Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Test Get Unread Notifications Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?unreadOnly=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Test Mark Notification as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/1/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Test Mark All Notifications as Read
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Test Get Unread Notification Count
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Test Invalid Notification ID (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/0/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Test Unauthorized Access (should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversations

### 15. Test Invalid User ID in Conversation (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/conversation/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

